  "description": "<p>It is easy to find room in your pack for a great night\u2019s sleep. Loaded with lofty down, the Bishop Pass sleeping bag has a lightweight quilt-like comfort, while still being super compressible. Using Mountain Hardwear\u2019s performance plus mummy profile, this bag hugs your body maximizing thermal efficiency.</p><ul><li>Shell is lightweight ripstop nylon, lining is soft woven nylon</li><li>DWR finish on the shell protects your bag from tent wall condensation and makes it easier to keep your bag clean</li><li>650 fill down is supplied by Allied traceable down and sourced under the Responsible Down Standard (80% down, 20% feather)</li><li>Down filled collar feels like a blanket and keeps warm air inside</li><li>Horizontal baffles wrap you in down and prevent the insulation from shifting and creating cold spots</li><li>Draft flap behind the anti-snag YKK\u00ae zipper ensures cold air doesn't sneak in</li><li>Hood lets you lift and move your head, even when fully zipped up and has a one-handed cinch adjustment</li><li>Internal stash pocket is a great place for your phone and a headlamp</li><li>Contoured footbox feels natural and roomy</li><li>Hang loops let you air it out in the sun</li><li>Includes a mesh storage bag and a nylon stuff sack</li></ul>",
